title: CONS EP Vol. 2 DJ MIX by Nick Catchdubs
description:
CONS EP Vol. 2 DJ MIX, mixed by DJ/producer/Fool’s Gold co-founder Nick Catchdubs, offers a sneak peak at all five songs from the second Converse CONS compilation. The EP was partially recorded at Converse Rubber Tracks in Brooklyn, New York. 

Mixed by: Nick Catchdubs 

In Order of Appearance:
Black Milk x BADBADNOTGOOD
Flatbush Zombies x Trash Talk
The Dillinger Escape Plan x Jarren Benton
Kevin Gates x Rustie 
Vince Staples x Bad Rabbits
